Package: standaRdized
Type: Package
Title: Standardized Index Calculation
Version: 1.0
Date: 2019-04-02
Author: Willem Maetens
Maintainer: Willem Maetens <w.maetens@vmm.be>
Depends: xts, FAdist, glogis
Imports: stats, fitdistrplus, lmomco, goftest
Suggests: grDevices, graphics
Description: This package provides functions and methods for the calculation of daily Standardized Index values such as the Standardized Precipitation Index (SPI), Standardized Precipitation Evapotranspiration Index (SPEI) or Standardized Streamflow Index (SSI)).
